    </section>

    <p>I have no doubt about Razer’s cor­po­rate smarts and that it is a proud Sin­ga­pore com­pany (Some firms buck trend and go ahead with plans for big­ger workspaces, Dec 7).</p>
    <p>I do not feel, how­ever, that it is cor­rect for the Sin­ga­pore flag (left) on the con­struc­tion hoard­ings of its new head­quar­ters to be painted in green in­stead of red. This is dis­re­spect­ful.</p>

